Document: ProgressBar
Path: godot/classes/class_progressbar.rst
Summary: A control node that visually represents a percentage, displaying fill status and optionally indeterminate progress.

Inherits: Range < CanvasItem < Node < Object

A control used for visual representation of a percentage. Shows the fill percentage in the center. Can also be used to show indeterminate progress. For more fill modes, use TextureProgressBar instead.
