Document: ProgressBar
Path: godot/classes/class_progressbar.rst
Summary: Describes the theme properties available for customizing the appearance of a ProgressBar node, including font colors, outline size, font styles, and background/fill styles.

Theme Property Descriptions
font_color (Color): The color of the text. Default: Color(0.95, 0.95, 0.95, 1).
font_outline_color (Color): The tint of text outline of the ProgressBar. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 1).
outline_size (int): The size of the text outline. Default: 0.
Note: If using a font with multichannel signed distance field enabled, its msdf pixel range must be set to at least twice the value of outline_size for outline rendering to look correct. Otherwise, the outline may appear to be cut off earlier than intended.
font (Font): Font used to draw the fill percentage if show_percentage is true.
font_size (int): Font size used to draw the fill percentage if show_percentage is true.
background (StyleBox): The style of the background.
fill (StyleBox): The style of the progress (i.e. the part that fills the bar).